snippet.title: Official Announcement Trailer Featuring Flo Rida! | Just Dance 4
snippet.description:
The world's #1 dance game brand is back with Just Dance 4! The latest edition of the record-breaking franchise takes the party to a whole new level of fun, with over 40 all-new hits, the coolest dances and brand new features!

Check out the official announcement trailer, featuring Flo Rida as well as some VERY special guest stars!
